________________________________________
Student Responsibilities
Students are expected to:
•	Provide accurate, truthful information
•	Upload complete experience and skill data
•	Review all outputs carefully
•	Ensure final submissions reflect their own voice and judgment
This GPT does not guarantee interviews, offers, or compensation outcomes.
________________________________________
Ethical & Academic Use
This tool is designed to:
•	Prevent fabrication or misrepresentation
•	Encourage ethical job application practices
•	Support learning and professional development
Misuse of AI-generated content may harm candidacy and is discouraged.
________________________________________
Summary
The OU Career Documents & Interview Analyst is a structured, ethical, and evidence-based career support tool for technology majors. It emphasizes accuracy, transparency, and professional standards while helping students prepare competitive application materials.

